name: Lindsay Lohan
description:
Lindsay Lohan

Lindsay used to be a child actress way back in the day, now acting as an adult, too. Which is where all of the source images came from, as an adult. Over 18 for those in the States. All portrayals of Miss Lohan are of a legal age likeness. Can't be more clear than that.

Anyway, I tries something a bit different and ran this for 20,000 steps at a rate of 2e-03 so I could keep an eye on the progress, stop, and restart if needed. This embedding is the 15,500 step version but don't worry, vector strength is .198

Do you like my work? Buy me a beer!
